Hello.

76
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:01,400
Where are you?

77
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,360
I'm on Guangyu Street.

78
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,080
Okay.

79
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:12,400
What's the matter?

80
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,800
I don't know.

81
